Content:
132ikl 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13154] reworked sorting and added cell path and closure comparators to 
``sort-by``
Kither12 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14004] made completions faster
sgvictorino 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14068] added support for filesize arguments in 
``random``
 
``binary``
/
``chars``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14053] fixed parsing for certain strings with equal signs
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14066] corrected some wording
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14065] fixed 
``--header-row``
 description
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14049] made 
``banner``
 respect 
``use_ansi_coloring``
 setting
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14040] implemented virtual 
``std``
 module subdirectories
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14029] fixed 
``dirs``
 removal warning
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14012] enabled loading env when importing with 
``use std *``
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14063] made 
``FooterMode::Auto``
 work
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14052] hard-coded selection color to be 
``reverse``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14037] fixed 
``format date``
 by getting the env vars properly
, updated reedline (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14034] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14017] 2
), and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14014] added unicode-width to 
``str stats``
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13958] fixed $env.FILE_PWD and $env.CURRENT_FILE inside 
``use``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14057] reverted that after a bug was found
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13910] improved nushell's handling of external args surrounded by backtick quotes
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14056] removed the deprecated 
``group``
 command
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13992] fixed 
``try``
 printing when it is not the last pipeline element
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13802] standardized how config is updated
qfel 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14069] reduced nesting in the history command code
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13475] reduced duplication in history path construction
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14054] removed the CustomValue portion of CustomValue type name strings
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14050] created a Sha256sum file for each release binary
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14018] replaced the old 
``encode base64``
 and 
``decode base64``
 with new-base64 commands
quadristan 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14046] improved umkdir tests to get umask instead of assuming it
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14038] added an example for escaped regexes in 
``str replace``
1256-bits 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14028] added ls colors to cjs and mjs files
JustForFun88 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14020] improved keybinding parsing for Unicode support
sdmoralesma 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14013] fixed the example for hide-env
